# IDLE — Visual System Reset (STRICT)

This document defines the EXACT visual rules for IDLE. No interpretation. No alternatives.

---

## 1. FONT RULES

**Font Family:** Arimo (Google Fonts)
**No fallbacks. No alternatives.**

| Usage | Weight |
|-------|--------|
| Headlines | Arimo SemiBold (600) |
| Body text | Arimo Regular (400) |
| Buttons | Arimo Medium (500) |
| Labels | Arimo Medium (500) |

**Import:**
```css
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Arimo:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');
```

**CSS:**
```css
font-family: 'Arimo', sans-serif;
```

---

## 2. COLOR TOKENS

### Backgrounds

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `--bg-primary` | `#E6E3DE` | Primary background (warm stone off-white) |
| `--bg-secondary` | `#DAD6D0` | Secondary background (foggy sand) |

### Text

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `--text-primary` | `#1F1F1F` | Primary text (soft charcoal) |
| `--text-secondary` | `#5A5A5A` | Secondary text (muted grey) |

### Dividers

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `--divider` | `#C9C5BF` | Hairlines, borders, separators |

### Accents

**NONE.**

If accent unavoidable: use `--text-primary` at reduced opacity.

### Forbidden Colors

- ANY green hue
- ANY pastel
- ANY saturated color
- ANY blue
- ANY "calming" color
- ANY wellness palette color

---

## 3. BACKGROUND IMAGE RULES

Background images are OPTIONAL.

### If Used, MUST Be:

- Desaturated to near-monochrome
- Blurred
- Low contrast
- Abstract only

### Allowed Subjects:

- Grey fog over water
- Snow texture
- Blurred stone surface
- Sand (desaturated)
- Overcast sky (grey only)

### Forbidden:

- Forests
- Leaves
- Grass
- Plants
- Mountains with detail
- Sunsets
- Any green imagery
- Wellness stock photos
- Nature landscapes

---

## 4. LIQUID GLASS RULES

Glass is FUNCTIONAL, not decorative.

### Treatment:

```css
.glass {
  background: rgba(230, 227, 222, 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border: 1px solid var(--divider);
  border-radius: 16px;
}
```

### Rules:

- Background blur: light (12px max)
- Opacity: low (70% max)
- No shine
- No gloss
- No reflections
- No shadows unless structural
- Rounded corners only if already present

### When In Doubt:

DO NOT USE GLASS.

---

## 5. LAYOUT RULES

### Structure:

- One primary column
- Centered vertically and horizontally
- Large margins (minimum 24px, prefer 40px+)
- No decorative containers
- No cards unless structurally required

### Hierarchy (exact order):

1. Title
2. One short supporting sentence
3. One primary action

Nothing else.

### Spacing Scale:

```
8px   — tight
16px  — base
24px  — comfortable
40px  — section
64px  — major division
```

---

## 6. REMOVED UI ELEMENTS

The following have been explicitly removed:

### Colors Removed:
- [x] `#1C1F1B` — green-tinted dark background
- [x] `#262B25` — green-tinted surface
- [x] `#1A1918` — dark charcoal background
- [x] `#252322` — dark surface
- [x] `rgba(20,24,20,...)` — green glass tints
- [x] All dark mode colors
- [x] All green hues
- [x] All nature-coded colors

### Imagery Removed:
- [x] Grass background (`/backgrounds/grass.jpg`)
- [x] `grassDrift` animation
- [x] Dark atmospheric gradients
- [x] Fog overlays (dark)
- [x] Nature-themed backgrounds

### UI Elements Removed:
- [x] Dark theme entirely
- [x] Green overlays
- [x] Nature-themed decoration
- [x] "Wellness" visual language
- [x] Warm color-based visual depth
- [x] Heavy glass effects
- [x] Decorative shadows

### Fonts Removed:
- [x] Inter font family
- [x] All fallback fonts

---

## 7. IMPLEMENTATION NOTES

### CSS Variables (exact):

```css
:root {
  --bg-primary: #E6E3DE;
  --bg-secondary: #DAD6D0;
  --text-primary: #1F1F1F;
  --text-secondary: #5A5A5A;
  --divider: #C9C5BF;
}
```

### Body Styles:

```css
body {
  background-color: var(--bg-primary);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  font-family: 'Arimo', sans-serif;
}
```

### Text Opacity (if accent needed):

```css
.muted { color: var(--text-primary); opacity: 0.5; }
.hint { color: var(--text-primary); opacity: 0.35; }
```

### Glass (minimal):

```css
.glass {
  background: rgba(230, 227, 222, 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border: 1px solid var(--divider);
  border-radius: 16px;
}
```

### No Background Image Default:

Background images removed by default. App uses solid `--bg-primary`.

---

## CONSTRAINTS (ABSOLUTE)

- Do NOT add features
- Do NOT suggest alternatives
- Do NOT interpret mood
- Do NOT introduce new colors
- Do NOT keep any green
- Do NOT use dark mode
- Do NOT use any font except Arimo

---

*Executed: January 2025*
